      right: ["Decompensated beta-cell failure: persistent hyperglycemia > 250 mg/dL despite oral agents", "Hyperosmolar hyperglycemic state (HHS): glucose > 600, severe dehydration, altered consciousness", "Acute MI or stroke (accelerated atherosclerosis from chronic insulin resistance)", "Severe hypertriglyceridemia > 500 mg/dL (risk of acute pancreatitis)", "Rapid unintentional weight loss suggesting advanced beta-cell failure"]
