      right: ["Severe hypoglycemia requiring assistance (sulfonylurea or insulin)", "Euglycemic DKA on SGLT2 inhibitor: nausea, vomiting, abdominal pain with glucose < 250 but ketones elevated", "Lactic acidosis on metformin: fatigue, myalgia, hyperventilation, abdominal pain (very rare)", "Acute pancreatitis on GLP-1 RA: severe epigastric pain radiating to back with elevated lipase", "A1C > 10% with catabolic symptoms requiring insulin initiation"]
