        correct: 1,
        rationale: "Add-back therapy with norethindrone acetate 5 mg daily is recommended to mitigate vasomotor symptoms and bone density loss caused by GnRH agonist-induced hypoestrogenism. It provides enough progestational effect to relieve symptoms without stimulating endometrial implant growth."
